
Auth Service :

//: Register a User
1. /auth/register

//: Create a token
2. /auth/token

//: Validate a token
3. /auth/validate

Train API :

//: To add a Train
1. api/trains/add

//: To search all train
2. api/search/all

//: To search a train based on date and boarding and destination station
3. api/search

//: To search Train Schedule based on date and trainId
4. /api/schedules/check

Reservation Service API :

//: To reserve a train (by filling reservation form)
1. /api/reservations/book

//: To cancel a reservation by pnr no.
2. /api/reservations/cancel/{pnr}